 # Where We Left Off - Mar 4, 2026
 
+## Session 76 (Mar 4, 2026) — Multi-Platform Marketplace + Dev Workflow Overhaul
+
+### Dev Workflow Change: Local Drive → GitHub Clone + Patch Ops
+Claude was crashing when connecting to the local mounted drive (`.git/index.lock` stuck, Word temp files `~$TODO.md`, large repo I/O over mount). Switched to a new workflow:
+- **Claude** clones from GitHub (`https://github.com/Fevit1/collectioncalc`), codes + commits in the clone
+- **Generates `.patch` files** to Mike's mounted drive
+- **Mike** applies patches in PowerShell: `git apply <patch> ; git add <files> ; git commit -m "msg" ; git push ; deploy ; purge`
+- This is now the standard workflow going forward
+
+### eBay Auction Validation Hardened
+- Fixed BIN validation: was only checking `> start_price`, now correctly checks `> reserve_price` when reserve is set
+- Fixed backend silently dropping invalid reserve/BIN prices → now returns explicit JSON error messages
+- Removed stale debug print "Get fulfillment policies: 400"
+- Fixed draft message: was "add photos and publish" → now "review and publish" (photos already uploaded)
+- Fixed "CollectionCalc" branding in `ebay_description.py` → "Slab Worthy"
+
+### eBay Username Fix Verified
+- Mike deployed the `commerce.identity.readonly` scope fix from Session 75
+- Disconnected and reconnected eBay to get new token with updated scope
+- Username now displaying correctly
+
+### Multi-Platform Marketplace Selling (Major Feature)
+Built a "Sell ▾" dropdown menu replacing individual eBay + Whatnot buttons. Supports 9 platforms total:
+
+| Platform | Type | API? | Integration |
+|----------|------|------|-------------|
+| **eBay** | Direct listing | Yes (Inventory API) | Full OAuth + publish |
+| **Whatnot** | Live auction | No | Prep tool (copy/paste) |
+| **Mercari** | Fixed price | No | Prep tool |
+| **Facebook Marketplace** | Fixed price | No | Prep tool |
+| **Heritage Auctions** | Consignment auction | No | Prep tool |
+| **ComicConnect** | Consignment auction | No | Prep tool |
+| **MyComicShop** | Consignment | No | Prep tool |
+| **COMC** | Consignment | No | Prep tool |
+| **Hip Comics** | Consignment auction | No | Prep tool |
+
+**How it works:**
+- Each platform gets AI-generated content (title, description, pricing, prep notes) optimized for its audience and format
+- Whatnot gets casual live-stream talking points; Heritage gets formal auction-house language
+- Generic modal adapts header color, pricing cards, and fields per platform
+- Copy individual fields or "Copy All" for pasting into platform dashboards
+- eBay still uses the direct listing modal with OAuth
+
+**New files created:**
+- `marketplace_prep.py` — Platform configs + AI content generator (8 platforms, Claude Sonnet 4)
+- `routes/marketplace.py` — Flask blueprint (`GET /platforms`, `POST /generate-content`)
+
+**Files modified:**
+- `collection.html` — Sell dropdown, generic marketplace prep modal (~540 lines changed)
+- `wsgi.py` — Marketplace blueprint registration
+- `ebay_listing.py` — Auction validation fixes
+- `ebay_description.py` — Branding fix
+
+### Patches Generated This Session
